text: FK Dračevo () is a Macedonian football club based in the town Dračevo in Skopje, North Macedonia. ==History== The club was founded in 2003, they are recently competed in the Macedonian Third League. ==References== ==External links== *Club info at MacedonianFootball *Macedonian Football Federation Category:Football clubs in North Macedonia Category:Football clubs in Skopje Category:Association football clubs established in 2003 Category:2003 establishments in the Republic of Macedonia
